    "Operation and Monitoring5.6.1 Log Analysis and Anomaly Detection.",
    "Several AI-driven anomaly detection approaches have been developed to detect anomalies in software systems.",
    "However, our investigation reveals the challenge that requires attention and resolution.",
    "Below, we introduce the challenge derived from previous studies with potential research opportunities.C14 -Normality Drift for Zero-Positive Anomaly Detection.",
    "In anomaly detection, zeropositive classification is commonly used because anomalies are typically rare and undefined."
